## Solution #2:

1. Cree un programa que le pida al usuario su nombre, apellido, y edad, y muestre si es un beb√©, ni√±o, preadolescente, adolescente, adulto joven, adulto, o adulto mayor.

name_string ‚Üí Input()

last_name_string ‚Üí Input()

age_int ‚Üí int (Input ()) - Para que retorne un int, si solo deja Input solo retorna textos. 

Print ‚Üí que es? ‚Äúmuestre‚Äù

```python
name = input('Add your name ')
last_name = input ('Add your last name ')
age = int (input ('Add your age '))
concatenate_string = (f' Your Name is ' + name + ' ' + last_name + ' ' + 'Your age is ' + str(age))
print (concatenate_string)
if (age <= 2):
    print ('You are a Baby')
elif (age <= 5):
    print ('You are a child')
elif (age <= 10):
    print ('You are a preadolescent')
elif (age <= 18):
    print ('You are a Teenager')
elif (age <= 25):
    print ('You are an Adult')
elif (age <= 65):
    print ('You are a Senior')
```

